   This file  is distributed under the  terms of the CeCILL  License (the
   text of which is in src/o64ml/ocamlclean/CeCILL-LICENSE-fr, in French,
   or  in src/o64ml/ocamlclean/CeCILL-LICENSE-en,  in English).   Article
